survivability planning algorithms and behaviors utilizing software integration lab (SIL) testing; improve modeling and simulation
tools and expertise in anticipation of team-based operations in complex future threat environments; update test, evaluation, and
data reduction capabilities in support of future army aircraft signature measurements and survivability assessments.
