quality data from the warfighter and networked sensors; developing validated and verified algorithms; and by developing machine
learning models for use by warfighters, to identify and quantify risk, effectively allocate and prioritize resources, and assess future
courses of action in support of logistics and sustainment operations in a contested environment.

FY 2026 Plans:
Will investigate maintenance data to include the full spectrum of information necessary to integrate multiple programs of record
including data streams for operations, personnel, and maintenance; validates different predictive modeling techniques which
increase decision making capabilities for the warfighter.
