cyber effects from Army tactical systems that are in RF proximity to adversary threat C2ISR capabilities. Research also focuses
on novel EW technique approaches to keep pace with new threats and provide greater portability across all applicable Army
systems. The effort will investigate new methodologies to counter adversary Intelligence Surveillance and Reconnaissance (ISR)
capabilities across multiple modalities.

FY 2026 Plans:
