This PE matures and demonstrates uncrewed air vehicles and mission system technologies as well as advanced teaming capabilities to enable unmanned aerial system
modernization. Emphasis is on developing aviation platform and mission system technologies to enhance uncrewed air vehicle combat and combat support operations
for attack, reconnaissance, air assault, survivability, logistics, and command and control missions. The PE will fund civilian salaries for in-house researchers/scientists
and program managers.

