 maintenance break/fixes, minor enhancements, software licenses, cyber compliance, program office contractor support, civilian salaries, DISA and migration to Cloud
 Hosting, and program office operations. IPPS-A now supports 1.1 million system users as of January 17, 2023.

D. Acquisition Strategy
The Integrated Personnel and Pay System-Army Increment II (IPPS-A Inc II) provides an integrated, multi-Component, personnel and pay system that streamlines
existing Human Resources (HR) systems and processes by enhancing efficiency and accuracy of personnel and pay procedures in support of 1.1 million Soldiers.

