A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
This project will mature and demonstrate Artificial Intelligence (AI) algorithms/models and supporting systems that leverage a team of air and ground sensors to
autonomously navigate and collaborate through shared perception of the optical, thermal, and electromagnetic spectrums to find, identify, geo-locate, track, and help
engage targets during reconnaissance missions. These technologies will produce a mix of fully integrated software, AI algorithms/models, and ground-based/aerial-
based drones to execute reconnaissance and engagement tasks in battlefield conditions.

