Description: Mature, integrate, and demonstrate advanced flight control technologies and state-of-the-art autonomy algorithms
that provide Future Vertical Lift (FVL) aircraft with enhanced maneuverability and agility, reduced cognitive workload, improved
survivability through damage tolerance, and the ability to operate on an autonomy spectrum from piloted to fully autonomous and
exploit degraded environments as a force multiplier.

