A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
This project matures and demonstrates engineering tools and high-fidelity modeling and simulation capabilities to predict and optimize weapon performance to ensure
lethality against structures and critical assets. This project provides validated engineering tools and technologies to rapidly evaluate and predict weapon performance.

 Work in this project complements Program Element (PE) 0602141A (Lethality Technology) / Project CF8 (Terminal Effects Against Critical Targets Tech).

 Work in this project is performed by the United States Army Engineer Research and Development Center Geotechnical and Structures Laboratory.

