This project matures and demonstrates an advanced network lethality architecture to enable Joint All Domain Command and Control decision aid algorithms for
coordinated and synchronized response and incorporates a full spectrum of effects and scalability to reduce the sensor to shooter timeline for Large Scale Combat
Operations.

